#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.59"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.59:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.59:0.2"
msgid "6. Sacittavagga"
msgstr "6. Your Own Mind"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.59:0.3"
msgid "59. Pabbajjāsutta"
msgstr "59. Going Forth"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.108"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.59:1.1"
msgid "“Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "“So you should train like this:"

msgctxt "an10.59:1.2"
msgid ""
"‘yathāpabbajjāparicitañca no cittaṃ bhavissati, na cuppannā pāpakā akusalā "
"dhammā cittaṃ pariyādāya ṭhassanti;"
msgstr ""
"‘Our minds will be consolidated as they were when we went forth, and arisen "
"bad unskillful qualities will not occupy our minds."

#. VAR: bhavañca → sambhavañca (bj, s2, s3, pts1) | samañca (s1)
msgctxt "an10.59:1.3"
msgid ""
"aniccasaññāparicitañca no cittaṃ bhavissati, anattasaññāparicitañca no "
"cittaṃ bhavissati, asubhasaññāparicitañca no cittaṃ bhavissati, "
"ādīnavasaññāparicitañca no cittaṃ bhavissati, lokassa samañca visamañca "
"ñatvā taṃsaññāparicitañca no cittaṃ bhavissati, lokassa bhavañca vibhavañca "
"ñatvā taṃsaññāparicitañca no cittaṃ bhavissati, lokassa samudayañca "
"atthaṅgamañca ñatvā taṃsaññāparicitañca no cittaṃ bhavissati, "
"pahānasaññāparicitañca no cittaṃ bhavissati, virāgasaññāparicitañca no "
"cittaṃ bhavissati, nirodhasaññāparicitañca no cittaṃ bhavissatī’ti—"
msgstr ""
"Our minds will be consolidated in the perceptions of impermanence, not-self, "
"ugliness, and drawbacks. Knowing what is just and unjust in the world, our "
"minds will be consolidated in that perception. Knowing about continued "
"existence and extermination of existence in the world, our minds will be "
"consolidated in that perception. Knowing the origination and ending of the "
"world, our minds will be consolidated in that perception. Our minds will be "
"consolidated in the perceptions of giving up, fading away, and cessation.’"

msgctxt "an10.59:1.4"
msgid "evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabbaṃ."
msgstr "That’s how you should train."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an10.59:2.1"
msgid ""
"Yato kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno yathāpabbajjāparicitañca cittaṃ hoti na "
"cuppannā pāpakā akusalā dhammā cittaṃ pariyādāya tiṭṭhanti, "
"aniccasaññāparicitañca cittaṃ hoti, anattasaññāparicitañca cittaṃ hoti, "
"asubhasaññāparicitañca cittaṃ hoti, ādīnavasaññāparicitañca cittaṃ hoti, "
"lokassa samañca visamañca ñatvā taṃsaññāparicitañca cittaṃ hoti, lokassa "
"bhavañca vibhavañca ñatvā taṃsaññāparicitañca cittaṃ hoti, lokassa "
"samudayañca atthaṅgamañca ñatvā taṃsaññāparicitañca cittaṃ hoti, "
"pahānasaññāparicitañca cittaṃ hoti, virāgasaññāparicitañca cittaṃ hoti, "
"nirodhasaññāparicitañca cittaṃ hoti, tassa dvinnaṃ phalānaṃ aññataraṃ phalaṃ "
"pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"When your minds are consolidated in these ten perceptions, you can expect "
"one of two results:"

msgctxt "an10.59:2.2"
msgid "diṭṭheva dhamme aññā, sati vā upādisese anāgāmitā”ti."
msgstr ""
"enlightenment in the present life, or if there’s something left over, non-"
"return.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.59:2.3"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
